sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  Client      ->> ShinyServer: request Shiny map app with a vector layer (Program Areas, Ecoregions, ...)
  ShinyServer ->> Client:      return JS with PMTiles URL (https://file.marinesensitivity.org/pmtiles/<layer>.pmtiles)
  loop for every tile in the current viewport
    Client     ->> Caddy:        HTTP range GET on the .pmtiles archive for tile {z}/{x}/{y}
    Caddy      ->> FileServer:   serve byte range from the static .pmtiles file on /share
    FileServer ->> Client:       return MVT bytes for the requested tile
    Note over Client: mapbox-gl renders + applies paint spec (fill-color, line-color) from match_expr
  end
%% mmdc -i diagrams/pmtiles.mmd --theme default --backgroundColor transparent --scale 8 -o diagrams/pmtiles.png
